Ludum Dare 24

The Singularity is Here!

Destroy the evil AI ships so you can plant the nuke at the central computer.

Hints:
* Use your movement keys to avoid the falling bullets.
* +1pt for every hit!
* -1pt for every miss.

Featuring:

* Three original characters made in GIMP.
* 13 original ships made in Alchemy.
* Original music made in LSDJ.
* Over 35 unique sound bytes.
* Tons of fun dialog.
* Awesome slash screens.
* Beautiful menus.
* Font made in fontstruct.
* Awesome sound effects effortlessly generated with bfxr.
* Crazy 3d like moving background thing.

